= SDL_GetDefaultCursor =

Get the default cursor.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
SDL_Cursor* SDL_GetDefaultCursor(void);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Return Value ==

Returns the default cursor on success or NULL on failure.



== Version ==

This function is available since SDL 2.0.0.



